## Locations

### Page
Contains a single screen
Used exclusively within Location Groups

### Location Group
Collection of pages
All pages share a commom info bar, actions menu, and sidebar
provides the structure and navigation for a group of related changes

### Wizard
ordered collection of screens
single info bar, actions menu, side bar
includes toolbar with next and back button

### Popup
Allows user to perform an interim action without leaving the context of the originl tasks
contains a single screen with the Return to <previous location> link
returns the user to the previous location after the popup is closed.

### Worksheet
rendered in the workspace frame
conatins a single screen

### Forward
Contains logic to execute before navigating to other locations
does not have screens

### Exit Point
Points to a URL outside of the Guidewire application
does not contain a screen widget



